== certbot ==
* https://certbot.eff.org/#debianjessie-apache

=== Install certbot ===
<syntaxhighlight lang=bash>
$ sudo apt-get install certbot
</syntaxhighlight>

=== Obtain / Renew certs ===
Dry-run:
<syntaxhighlight lang=bash>
$ sudo certbot renew --dry-run
</syntaxhighlight>

Update:
<syntaxhighlight lang=bash>
$ sudo certbot renew
</syntaxhighlight>

Add to root's cron and check twice daily:
<syntaxhighlight lang=bash>
0 3,15 * * * certbot renew --quiet 
</syntaxhighlight>

